  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueGenerator<Address>

    public class AddressBuilder
extends com.guidewire.pl.domain.contact.AddressBuilderBase<Address,AddressBuilder>
    Builder class for an Address. Typical usage: 
       new AddressBuilder().createAndCommit()
    which creates an Address with some default values.
